[normal]Accordingly [bold]Boroughs themselves will respond on the other four CLG questions directly.[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]Collaborative Protocol[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]In managing WLA multi borough procurements we adopt a protocol that requires 
[normal]the nomination of a lead borough for
[normal]; 
[normal]p
[normal]rocurement
[normal], legal service, financial 
[normal]advice, technical specification, HR, TUPE, IT, quality, safety and environment.
[normal]  
[normal]The lead borough may be different for each discipline and each project. 
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]The protocol requires that we place our collective trust on the integrity and robustness of the lead 
[normal]boroughs internal policies
[normal], 
[normal]processes 
[normal]and people 
[normal]to ensure rectitude.
[normal] 
